data.title: Finding aid for the Vertical Files
data.text: Abstract: Subject files created by the Archives & Special Collections staff on topics frequently researched. Primarily, these files were created during the 1970s; however staff devotion decreased during the 1980s and the files stopped receiving additions. Note: William Faulkner not listed in this inventory. General information on the state's authors, including their literary awards. (See also Poets)
